was on Reiden's payroll.

18:55.509 --> 18:56.635
Okay.

18:57.303 --> 18:59.431
Reiden has an office
here in Paris.

19:00.473 --> 19:01.850
We're breaking in.

19:15.946 --> 19:18.586
JACKSON: So the Paris Reiden ofHce
only handles European contracts,

19:18.699 --> 19:22.249
