Shafer was on their payroll.

19:27.500 --> 19:29.753
And how are we gonna do that?

19:29.919 --> 19:32.422
What, the hacking-into-the-system
part or the proving-it part?

19:32.588 --> 19:34.056
CHLOE: Both.

19:34.674 --> 19:35.846
Here.

19:36.133 --> 19:38.306
It makes more sense
if you drink this.

19:38.469 --> 19:40.813
Okay. Uh, second part first.

