be a team effort.

20:39.572 --> 20:41.540
Even Mitch.

20:41.699 --> 20:45.579
We're presuming there are thousands
of documents to comb through,

20:45.745 --> 20:47.213
so we're going to
copy the records

20:47.371 --> 20:50.341
onto a computer with
enough storage space.

20:50.499 --> 20:51.921
The one in the animal lab.

20:52.460 --> 20:53.507
And what's my role?

20:54.086 --> 20:56.259
You get to have some fun.

21:00.676 --> 21:02.804
