in les Hauts-de-Seine.

28:10.814 --> 28:12.316
JACKSON: So if he's
not headed home,

28:13.525 --> 28:14.965
he's headed towards
the other bears.

28:15.110 --> 28:18.034
Listen, you know how we talked
about the bears changing?

28:18.197 --> 28:22.202
Well, I think they've developed
some kind of endoskeleton.

28:22.367 --> 28:23.835
- What do you mean?
- A hard shell,

28:23.994 --> 28:26.088
like a hard shell
underneath its skin.

28:26.246 --> 28:28.044
Wait a minute, a shell?

28:28.207 --> 28:30.175
