28:41.094 --> 28:43.438
What are you doing here?
Told you I was fine.

28:43.597 --> 28:46.225
Well, I came to make sure you
were as fine as you said you were.

28:46.391 --> 28:49.565
- Well, you missed quite a party.
JAMIE: Yeah, I can see that.

28:50.187 --> 28:52.610
Hey,
that's a nice little scratch.

28:52.773 --> 28:55.697
- I know, it's hot, right?
JACKSON: Okay.

28:55.859 --> 28:59.284
We're at the forest, Mitch,
northwest corner. Where's the bear?

29:00.405 --> 29:02.282
In the woods.

29:02.449 --> 29:03.701
Due west of you.

29:03.867 --> 29:05.460
Looks like about...

29:05.619 --> 29:07.667
500 yards in.

