experimenting with?

29:32.938 --> 29:33.985
No.

29:35.274 --> 29:36.742
No!

29:36.900 --> 29:39.494
Still no leads on the
other three bears?

29:39.653 --> 29:42.202
No, but Park Service
is going to Cordon off

29:42.364 --> 29:43.991
