[IN FRENCH]

35:49.564 --> 35:51.066
[IN FRENCH]

36:16.091 --> 36:18.594
[SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

36:28.019 --> 36:31.944
This is the DNA profile
of our bear from the lab.

36:33.066 --> 36:36.661
And this is the
same bear's DNA...

36:37.237 --> 36:40.286
six years ago,
when he was first tagged.

36:40.448 --> 36:41.620
- It changed. MITCH: Mm-hm.

36:41.783 --> 36:43.410
Because of the Mother Cell.

36:43.576 --> 36:46.295
- Uh, yes and no.
- What does that mean?

36:46.454 --> 36:48.206
MITCH: Okay,
think of it this way.

36:48.373 --> 36:50.751
None of the Earth's
creatures are born perfect.

36:50.917 --> 36:53.136
Right?
We all have genetic anomalies.

36:53.294 --> 36:56.468
Be it a birthmark,
double-jointed wrists, webbed toes.

36:56.631 --> 36:59.510
But the anomalies
that become the norm

36:59.676 --> 37:00.973
are the ones that are adaptive.

37:01.136 --> 37:04.766
That are more useful to
survival, like opposable thumbs.

37:04.931 --> 37:06.774
What does it have
to do with animals?

37:07.976 --> 37:09.478
The traits we've seen.

37:09.644 --> 37:11.191
The bear's endoskeleton,

37:11.354 --> 37:13.322
the bats flying abnormally high,

37:13.481 --> 37:15.859
Iions seemingly communicating
over long distances...

37:16.025 --> 37:18.744
They all make their species
more capable of survival.

37:18.903 --> 37:21.281
- Stronger, better.
- And what I think...

37:21.781 --> 37:24.830
Just like our ancestors
developed opposable thumbs,

37:24.993 --> 37:28.588
I think the Mother Cell is just
accelerating these mutations

37:28.747 --> 37:31.341
in the animal kingdom that
we would see occur naturally,

37:31.499 --> 37:34.173
but not for another
several generations.

37:34.335 --> 37:35.837
Maybe a couple hundred
years from now,

37:36.004 --> 37:38.190
depending on how long it takes
us to screw up the planet.

37:38.214 --> 37:41.138
But we're seeing it now
because of the Mother Cell.

37:41.301 --> 37:42.803
But here's the good news.

37:42.969 --> 37:47.145
If the Mother Cell can make a
naturally-occurring situation worse,

37:47.640 --> 37:48.812
maybe it can do the opposite.

37:49.642 --> 37:50.689
M ITCH: Correct.

37:50.852 --> 37:53.196
But what's the opposite?

37:53.688 --> 37:56.032
The Mother Cell can
cure the animals?

