38:21.674 --> 38:24.518
And if you're not happy with the
way I'm handling my assignment,

38:24.677 --> 38:26.270
you can feel free to replace me.

38:26.429 --> 38:29.353
But until then, now that I know
what's happening to the animals,

38:29.516 --> 38:31.359
I am gonna try to do
my best to reverse it.

38:32.060 --> 38:33.983
If that's okay with you.

38:35.605 --> 38:37.858
You surprise me,
Miss Tousignant.

38:40.610 --> 38:42.283
Thank you.

39:04.634 --> 39:06.932
I believe you're waiting for me.

39:08.721 --> 39:10.519
I'm Clayton Burke.

